 A man was killed last night following an apparent hit-and-run on the N4 highway outside of Machadodorp in Mpumalanga. ER24 paramedics were returning to their branch in the evening when they were flagged down by the local authorities who were closing off a lane. ER24 spokesman Russel Meiring said that upon closer inspection, paramedics discovered the body of a man lying in the middle of the lane. Local authorities were on the scene for further investigations.    